## 🟠 Major Bugs (P1)

### Bug 4: Three Homepage Nav Links Are Dead (`href="#"`)
- **Severity**: 🟠 Major
- **Location**: [page.tsx (landing)](file:///Users/piyushsharma/Projects/Project%203%20Prior%20Auth%20Pipeline/src/app/page.tsx#L24-L26)
- **Description**: The homepage nav bar has three links that all point to `href="#"`:
  - "Pipeline Visualizer" → `#`
  - "Analytics" → `#`
  - "Human Review" → `#`
- **Impact**: Clicking any of these scrolls to top of page, doing nothing. These should either link to their console equivalents (`/console/visualizer`, etc.) or be removed.

### Bug 5: "View Documentation" Button Does Nothing
- **Severity**: 🟠 Major
- **Location**: [page.tsx (landing)](file:///Users/piyushsharma/Projects/Project%203%20Prior%20Auth%20Pipeline/src/app/page.tsx#L62-L64)
- **Description**: The button is a plain `<button>` with no `onClick` handler and no wrapping `<Link>`. It renders correctly but clicking it produces zero behavior.
  ```tsx
  <button className="px-8 py-4 bg-neutral-900 ...">View Documentation</button>
  ```
- **Impact**: Dead CTA on the landing page hero section

### Bug 6: No Form Validation on New Request
- **Severity**: 🟠 Major
- **Location**: [RequestForm.tsx](file:///Users/piyushsharma/Projects/Project%203%20Prior%20Auth%20Pipeline/src/components/dashboard/RequestForm.tsx)
- **Description**: All 7 form inputs have `required: false`. The form can be submitted completely empty. There's:
  - No `required` attributes on any input
  - No client-side validation logic
  - No error states shown to the user
  - DOB field uses `type="text"` with placeholder "YYYY-MM-DD" instead of `type="date"`
  - NPI field accepts any text instead of enforcing 10-digit numeric
- **Impact**: Garbage data can be submitted to the backend

