## 🟡 Minor Bugs (P2)

### Bug 7: Hamburger Menu Button (Mobile) Does Nothing
- **Severity**: 🟡 Minor
- **Location**: [DashboardLayout.tsx](file:///Users/piyushsharma/Projects/Project%203%20Prior%20Auth%20Pipeline/src/components/dashboard/DashboardLayout.tsx#L26-L28)
