### Bug 8: Notification Bell Button Does Nothing
- **Severity**: 🟡 Minor
- **Location**: [DashboardLayout.tsx](file:///Users/piyushsharma/Projects/Project%203%20Prior%20Auth%20Pipeline/src/components/dashboard/DashboardLayout.tsx#L51-L54)
