### Bug 9: Search Box Is Non-functional
- **Severity**: 🟡 Minor
- **Location**: [DashboardLayout.tsx](file:///Users/piyushsharma/Projects/Project%203%20Prior%20Auth%20Pipeline/src/components/dashboard/DashboardLayout.tsx#L34-L39)
