### Bug 10: History Page Filter/Download Buttons Are Unlabeled
- **Severity**: 🟡 Minor
- **Location**: Console History page
- **Description**: Two icon-only buttons (filter funnel icon, download icon) on the History page have:
  - No `aria-label` attribute
  - No text content
  - No tooltip on hover
- **Impact**: Accessibility issue — screen readers cannot identify these buttons

### Bug 11: 12 SVGs Without `aria-hidden` or Labels
- **Severity**: 🟡 Minor
